title: Falling for Him 5
description: Rachel and Peter are planning their wedding - too bad they can't agree even on the tiniest details. Soon they get into their first big fight and Rachel runs out of the door. After they make up, their lives are all roses, until a person from the past comes to haunt Rachel. Can she and Peter find out what Ed is up to? Can they stop him before he sabotages their wedding?
author: Jessica Gray
